Fear not , I am with thee , O be not dismayed , For I am thy God , and will still give thee aid ; I'll strengthen thee , help thee , and cause thee to stand ,
Upheld by my righteous , omnipotent hand .
Upheld by my righteous , omnipotent hand .
When through the deep waters I call thee to go ,
The rivers of wo shall not thee overflow ;
When through the deep waters I call thee to go , The rivers of wo shall not thee overflow ;
For I will be with thee , thy troubles to bless ,
And sanctify to thee thy deepest distress .
For I will be with thee , thy troubles to bless , And sanctify to thee thy deepest distress .
When through fiery trials thy pathway shall lie ,
My grace , all - sufficient , shall be thy supply ;
The flames shall not hurt thee , I only design ,
Thy dross to consume , and thy gold to refine .
When through fiery trials thy pathway shall lie , My grace , all - sufficient , shall be thy supply ; The flames shall not hurt thee , I only design , Thy dross to consume , and thy gold to refine .
Even down to ol age , all my people shall prove ,
And when hoary hairs shall their temples adorn ,
Like lambs shall they still in my bosom be borne .
Even down to ol age , all my people shall prove , My sovereign , eternal , unchangeable love ; And when hoary hairs shall their temples adorn , Like lambs shall they still in my bosom be borne .
The soul that on Jesus doth lean for repose ,
The soul that on Jesus doth lean for repose ,
I will not , I will not desert to his foes ;
I will not , I will not desert to his foes ;
That soul , tho ' all hell should endeavor to shake ,
I'll never , no never , no never forsake .
That soul , tho ' all hell should endeavor to shake , I'll never , no never , no never forsake .
Guide me , O thou great Jehovah ,
I am weak , but thou art mighty ,
Hold me with thy powerful hand ;
Feed me till I want no more .
Feed me till I want no more .
